Show Notes:
- &#039;Petrified&#039; was over &#039;Points Of Authority&#039;. &#039;There They Go&#039; was over the outro. 
- The band finally did a full, complete setlist again. It seems Chester was fully recovered for this show.
- During the break between the two encores, the crowd started chanting for &#039;Bleed It Out&#039;. The band then came out and played the song, which was pretty cool.
- It seems Brad cut his finger at the end of the show. A fan has said that they saw him go up to a camera at the end of the show and hold his finger really close to it. 

Info taken from www.lplive.net - The Linkin Park Live Guide
